name: StaticBucketMap_sizeTest
description: Unit tests for the size method of the StaticBucketMap class.

test_cases.name: testSizeEmptyMap
test_cases.description: Tests the size method when the map is empty.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterPut
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding a single entry to the map.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterMultiplePuts
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding multiple entries to the map.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterRemove
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding and then removing an entry from the map.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterClear
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding entries and then clearing the map.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterPutAndRemoveDifferentBuckets
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding entries and removing one from a different bucket.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterPutAndRemoveSameBucket
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding entries and removing both from the same bucket.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterPutAndRemoveNonExistentKey
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding an entry and attempting to remove a non-existent key.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterPutNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding an entry with a null key.

test_cases.name: testSizeAfterRemoveNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests the size method after adding an entry with a null key and then removing it.
